<H3> <TI>   Paper Notes U.S. Tilt Toward Pakistan </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Paper Notes U.S. Tilt Toward Pakistan </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2003071894 Bombay NAVBHARAT TIMES in Hindi 12 Mar 94 p 4 </F>
<F P=103> BK2003071894 </F>
<F P=104>  Bombay NAVBHARAT TIMES </F>
<F P=105>  Hindi </F>


