<H3> <TI>   Russian Embassy Employee Killed South of Algiers </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Embassy Employee Killed South of Algiers </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Fourth Russian Killed in Six Months </H4>

<F P=102> NC2803165894 Paris AFP in English 1653 GMT 28 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2803165894 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Algiers, March 28 (AFP) -- A Russian embassy 
employee was murdered Monday at Saoula, south of the capital, 
the fourth Russian slain in the North African country in six 
months, security officials said. 
  Two Frenchmen were slain last week, victims of the war being 
waged by Islamic fundamentalists against the military-led 
government. More than 30 foreigners have been killed in the 
country in the past six months. 

</TEXT>

