<H4>    Security Kills Four of Six Assassins; Another Murder </H4>

<F P=102> LD2903201094 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 
GMT 29 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2903201094 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers ENTV Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] A communique from the security services said that 
the security forces killed 20 terrorists, and a number of others 
were arrested last Saturday [26 March] and Sunday. 
  The security services also said that four out of the six 
terrorists who carried out the assassination of the Russian 
diplomat and a member of the Foreign Ministry were killed 
yesterday. 
  The communique from the security services added that the 
director of the Algerian Red Crescent of Sidi Rached, in Tipaza 
province, was killed near his home yesterday by two terrorists. 
Another citizen was also killed in Tiaret. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

