BFN 

  [Text] Security authorities have announced that Touati 
Belkacem, deputy director of the African section at the Foreign 
Ministry, was assassinated this morning in front of his home 
near Bordj El Kifan in the suburbs of the capital. The victim 
was attacked by three men armed with automatic pistols as he was 
preparing to leave his house. The same source added that his 
