<H3> <TI>   Three Arrested for 25 February Stabbing of Russian Nationals </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Three Arrested for 25 February Stabbing of Russian Nationals </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN3003090994 Amman AKHIR KHABAR in Arabic 28-29 Mar 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> JN3003090994 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman AKHIR KHABAR </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


